title: Grateful Dead Live at Carolina Stadium - University of South Carolina on 1985-10-31
venue: Carolina Stadium - University of South Carolina
lineage: SBD > Master Cassette > Reel > DAT (48khz) > Sony R500 > SEK'D Prodif Plus > Samplitude v7.02 Professional > SHN > Mitsui CDR > EAC > WAV > FLAC16
description:
Set 1: Spooky Space > Werewolves of London, The Music Never Stopped, West L.A. Fadeaway, Mama Tried, Mexicali Blues, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain, Might As Well 

Set 2: Shakedown Street, Playin' In The Band > Ship of Fools > Space > Drumz > Space > Dear Mr. Fantasy > Not Fade Away 

Encore: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text:
great mix! This show was a few of my friends first. The audience's are fair and the SBD's are over saturated. This is the best sound quality of this night I have found. Check out the Looks Like Rain and Ship of Fools!!!

 Four skulls for quality!
